Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:57.52,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}We watched the fading contrails go by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:20:04.45,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}They were so dazzling, I ran away - I was always weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:09.09,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}I let go, frustrated by the fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:16.88,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}...that I couldn't stay unchanged since that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:26.95,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}...couldn't stay unchanged forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:34.88,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}That bird still can't fly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:41.35,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}But someday I'll know the feeling of gliding through the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:50.63,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}The place I can't reach is still far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.63,0:20:57.12,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}I gaze at it with a wish locked away inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:21:05.50,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}The children walk on the summer railway tracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:13.43,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}exposing their bare feet to the blowing wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:21.27,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}We place in the distance the days of our childhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:27.80,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}with hope that will take flight in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:35.64,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}I chased and chased the fading contrails.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:44.90,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Nothing changed since the day we went past that hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:51.50,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}I hope we can be our honest selves forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:22:07.87,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}and definitely protect this Poseidon-like strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.91,0:00:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this? Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I was with someone until just a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With someone very important...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good. My head is foggy and I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.89,0:00:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come from? Where is your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's okay to leave it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll walk away a little and turn around. If he doesn't follow me, then I'll leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:00:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get set, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, wanna go to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.34,0:01:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sure! My bathing suit this year is super daring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.35,0:01:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mustn't cry. Hold it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be all alone again this summer, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't get anyone to play with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all know about it... that I'm not a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:01:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that person from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't want to be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a long vacation... I don't want to be the only one all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to try talking to that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he seems like a nice person, I'll ask him to play with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep smiling, now, and try to act natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ramen set!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you do seem to have pluck. I like that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Yukito is a really nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500}Alright. He can stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kano Kirishima. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kunisaki Yukito.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have some free time, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'll name you Freefreeplanetling Number 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Number 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me! And Potato is Number 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what do Freefreeplanetlings do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just have time on their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the fate of all Freefreeplanetlings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? We have nothing to do, do we, Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohno Minagi-san. She's my classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's smart. She's at the top of our grade, and she's president of the Astronomy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukito is flying like a leaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nothing unusual. I have them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A strange dream about the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:04:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the sky. It was a world I'd never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, when you sit like this, the clouds are above you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in my dream, the clouds were below my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could see the blue of the sea between the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't tell how far it was to there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything went on into infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kano taking a nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, because of last night too, I told her to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel anxious... sort of nostalgic, and sort of melancholy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that plume, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's let it go to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I will keep it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take good care of it, Minagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl with wings continues to have sad dreams in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if you find her, please tell her many happy things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And set her free from her sad dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you smiling now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, keep smiling. Say bye-bye while smiling for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you smiling, Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sad to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not sad. I'm smiling, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru, bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? Do you feel sick or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.40,0:08:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay! I'm okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's done that ever since she was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right when I think she's making a friend, it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got dizzy all of a sudden and my feet got tangled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I made you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're slightly anaemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do? Do you want to go to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll be alright. I think I just need some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yukito-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a connection between the person you're looking for and my dreams, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know... Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my other self in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, she is suffering now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to try to see more dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if I do that, they might help me understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, maybe I can help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I should leave soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay with you any longer, neither one of us will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I've decided to run away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, bye-bye. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too. Stay strong. Stay strong, even if you're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll do my best even if I'm alone. I'm a strong girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent. Bye, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been alone until today. And I'll be alone from now on, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I do my best, I just cause trouble for other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not a single good thing about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:10:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've just continued to be alone, like I've always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should never have come to love someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if I never wake up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? I thought I wouldn't be able to get up anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito! Where are you? You came back, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:10:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san... Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, so please don't go anywhere. Stay by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a strong girl, so I'm sure you'll be able to reach it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that goal that no one else has been able to reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be near you. I'll never forget you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:12:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito! Wait! Don't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay strong until you reach the goal, Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll do my best. Let's do our best, Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream about the person I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san came back to me in the end after all, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave me something precious, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's rest for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll have my usual; the weird juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a tough time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked very hard to keep you here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be taken to the Tachibana residence someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I ignored you even though we lived together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be hard for us to separate if I fell in love with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.91,0:13:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always kept my feelings subdued so that I will be fine no matter when you leave, but there was no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lie to myself any longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I've decided. I'll make you my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was on my knees in front of the Tachibana residence the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I had more patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:14:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I felt like I had to show off for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I raised my hand even though I didn't know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came and gave me a whack in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're up, Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Are you still sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, oba-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu, I'm your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, say "thank you" to your aunty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keisuke! Wait, Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three days. Please wait three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If, at that time, she says she doesn't want to stay with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's okay. You can take Misuzu away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three days...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I regain our mother-child relationship in that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be happy if I can just spend one day with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:16:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the sea... beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so far. How many years did it take us to get here, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could have enjoyed this beautiful view anytime we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world were we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it alright now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's heavy. It's been a long time since you carried her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to you that she's grown this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah... Let her hold on to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She loves this doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She should be able to sleep comfortably if she's holding this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's still fussy, give her this to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her favourite juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fool! What is he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I'm your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer vacation, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer vacation for just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.13,0:18:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's okay. We can play together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Mum. I want you to go ahead a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Is there a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Take Sora with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.30,0:18:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, Misuzu. I'm over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did my best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can go to my goal now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you tired already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, after you reach me, we'll go home and play cards or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... My goal, the goal I've been aiming at for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... did my best, so it's enough now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can rest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:19:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was able to finish everything, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll go to my goal, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time... the summer vacation when I thought I'd do my best,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the summer vacation that started on the day I met Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though lots happened, even though it hurt sometimes or was painful sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I tried my hardest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying it all starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goal!
